('bookkeeper-moex-01162', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-105-12108af6', 'sub-bookkeeper-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '已充任記帳士者，依民國105年11月9日最新修正公布之記帳士法，下列何者構成撤銷或廢止其記帳士 證書之法定情事？', '["經公立醫院證明有精神病者", "因殺人罪而判刑確定者", "受破產之宣告尚未復權者", "受本法所定除名處分者"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "bd3eaadefb1c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9b2da7a32888", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105170", "c": "602", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "記帳相關法規概要", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年建築師技師第二次食品技師不動產經紀人記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
